Alright, now to our smoothie I am also going
to add some ground flax which is lovely for

00:03:27.239 --> 00:03:34.769
omega-3. Now I put water to make my smoothie
go round. You can also use any kind of non-dairy

00:03:34.769 --> 00:03:41.040
